  "title": "Fulfilment Planner Executive",
  "description": "<ul><li><p><strong>Well Established Company</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Basic $3000 - $3800 + AWS + Variable Bonus</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Excellent Welfare and Benefits + Career progression</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Working location: East</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Working day: Monday to Friday</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Working hours: 8.00am to 5.30pm</strong></p></li></ul><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>To coordinate and manage Purchase Order requirements</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>To manage, plan, analyse and oversea demand & supply commitments</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>To communicate with customers and internal teams</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>To be responsible in managing customers’ accounts, driving shipment/revenue, reviewing on raw materials requirements, customer forecast/requirements</strong></p></li><li><p>Implement new processes to support the changing needs of the company</p></li><li><p>Manage product configurations and BOMs with JO database</p></li><li><p>To support business/department requirements through the preparation and analysis of reports</p></li><li><p>Perform other assigned duties</p></li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Possess minimum Nitec, Diploma qualification with 1-2 years of experience in material planning or production planning, preferably in the manufacturing industry</p></li></ul><p>Candidates are encouraged to apply this position via <strong>Apply Now </strong>button with the following information in the resume</p><ul><li><p>Work experiences and job responsibilities</p></li><li><p>Current and Expected salary</p></li><li><p>Reason for leaving</p></li><li><p>Date of availability</p></li><li><p>Education background</p></li></ul><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p><p>LIONG ZHAO GUAN (R22107632)</p><p>EA Recruitment Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 21C0492</p>",
